* Version 0.1.0 (released 2014-03-18)

  * Stable version tested on
    - Windows 8 / 8.1 / 7 (x64)
    - Linux Ubuntu 12.04
    - Mac OSX Mountain Lion / Mavericks

* Version 0.0.6 (released 2014-03-17)
  
  * New MultiReader support
    - detect the NEO over multiple readers
    - improved patch for mac osx
    - minor fix

* Version 0.0.5 (released 2014-03-11)

  * New Mac OSX
  - Fixed icons
  - Fixex Yubikey NEO support by adding a custom patch to edit Info.plist
  - CCID TOOLS should not be needed anymore

* Version 0.0.4 (released 2014-03-05)

  * Fixed a bug that was causing Yubico logo not to display correctly

* Version 0.0.3 (released 2014-03-05)

  * New Features:
    - OSX PKG
    - Fixed .spec file added .icns

* Version 0.0.2 (released 2014-02-26)

  * New Features:
    - Menu Bar
    - Ability to set a password
 
* Version 0.0.1 (released 2014-02-19)

  * Initial release supporting mode changing.